0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9408:\"<h2>Joomla Logo Slider Can Display a List of Client, Supporter, Team, Partner, Sponsor or Brand Logo in Your Joomla website. Control Almost Everything from Strong Administrator Settings.</h2>\n<p>Logo Slider is a Responsive and Easy to Implement Joomla Logo Showcase With and Without Carousel Slider. This Extension Can Display a List of Clients, Supporters, Partners or Sponsors Logo in Your Website with CSS3 Based Parallax Scrolling Background Effect and Image Overlay Color. Also You Can Create a Grid of Images with Suitable Links. This Logo Showcase Module Works Great on Mobiles and Tablets. You can Control number of  Displayable Slides Item According Device.</p>\n<h4>Display Unlimited Number of Brand or Client Logo By Repeated Field Group ( Add New ) with Auto Play and Infinity Slides loop.</h4>\n<div class=\"lgx-product-section-header\">\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-angellist\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Exclusive Feature</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> 100% Responsive and mobile friendly.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Touch Friendly Slides with Infinity Slides loop.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Control Displayable Slides Item According Device Width( Viewport) </div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Multiple Instances on One Page.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Control Section Width, Margin, Padding.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Touch swipe navigation.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Tooltips enable and disable option.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i>  Tooltip font size, color, background color change options.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Set Custom Image or Text Navigation button.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i>  Custom Section Title with Style options.</div>\n</p></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> 60+ Special CSS3 Animation Effects.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Parallax Scrolling background with  Overlay Color and Opacity.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Simple Showcase  and Slider Layout.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i>  Active Logo Animation Effects.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Set Image or Text Navigation button.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i>  Style(CSS) Overrides Available form Template.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Customizable Slides direction ( Left an Right).</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i>  Touch and Drag Support.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i>  Strong Administrator Settings (110+ Options).</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Joomla 3.7 Ready &#038; Multi-lingual Supported.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Touch and Swipe enabled so works great on devices like iPhone, iPad, Blackberry, Android etc.</div>\n</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"lgx-margin-md\"></div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>  Random Logo Display Available .</li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Unlimited Logos Clients.</li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Background Image &#038; color for Slider Area. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Control Slider Pagination Color. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Set Image or Text Navigation button. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Control Dots navigation and prev/next buttons. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Editable styles with pure CSS or LESS. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Customize style with available Gulp File. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Super lightweight.</li>\n</ul></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Touch swipe navigation. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Slider auto pause On Hover. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Strong Administrator Settings. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Excellent CSS3 Transitions </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Valid HTML &#038; SEO friendly. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Supports all the modern browsers. </li>\n<li><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Support and Free upgrade. </li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"lgx-product-section-header\">\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-eye\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Product Screenshot</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row text-center\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12\">\n        <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/1.png\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"product-img\" src=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/1.png\" alt=\"Product Image\" /></a>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\" style=\"margin: 10px 0\"></div>\n<div class=\"row text-center\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\n        <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/2.png\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"product-img\" src=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/2.png\" alt=\"Product Image\" /></a>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\n        <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/3.png\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"product-img\" src=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/3.png\" alt=\"Product Image\" /></a>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\" style=\"margin: 10px 0\"></div>\n<div class=\"row text-center\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\n        <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/4.png\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"product-img\" src=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/4.png\" alt=\"Product Image\" /></a>\n    </div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6\">\n        <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/5.png\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"product-img\" src=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/screenshot/657/5.png\" alt=\"Product Image\" /></a>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix\" style=\"margin: 10px 0\"></div>\n<div class=\"row text-cente