p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Content Slider Advanced is a Carousel slider Module that allows to display your joomla article with stunning and unique look as well as incredible functionality.</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Content Slider Advanced</strong> is a Responsive carousel slider module with touch swipe navigation. This module allows slide your articles from Joomla! or K2 categories with image &#038; stunning design. The module&#8217;s rich &#038; user-friendly back-end configuration provides more control over the module.<br />\n            Content Slider Advanced also supports YouTube or Vimeo videos that helps to display your video galleries.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 id=\"item-description__exclusive-features\">Exclusive Features</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Joomla 3.7 Ready</li>\n<li>Responsive &#038; Touch Friendly Slides.</li>\n<li>Multiple Instances on One Page.</li>\n<li>Control Displayable Slides Item According Device Width(Viewport)</li>\n<li>Display Slides Card With Material Design.</li>\n<li>Support Joomla content and K2 content</li>\n<li>Easy and elegant display of article.</li>\n<li>Three Different layout are available: Default, Card and Material Card.</li>\n<li>Show multiple slides in a carousel layout.</li>\n<li>Style(CSS) Overrides available form Template </li>\n<li>Fully Responsive &#038; Mobile Ready Slides Card.</li>\n<li>Control visibility of Card Title, Image &#038; Text.</li>\n<li>Display Slides with Article Title, Intro Image &#038; Text</li>\n<li>Display Full Article Content.</li>\n<li>Support YouTube/Vimeo videos.</li>\n<li>Background color for Slider Area.</li>\n<li>Control Slider Pagination Color.</li>\n<li>Set Image or Text  Navigation button.</li>\n<li>Control Dots navigation and prev/next buttons.</li>\n<li>Infinity Slides loop.</li>\n<li>Touch swipe navigation</li>\n<li>Slider auto pause OnHover</li>\n<li>Customizable Slides direction</li>\n<li>Carousel Slider</li>\n<li>Touch and Drag Support.</li>\n<li>Strong Administrator Settings </li>\n<li>Excellent CSS3 Transitions</li>\n<li>Valid HTML &#038; SEO friendly</li>\n<li>Editable styles with pure CSS or LESS ( Gulp File is available )</li>\n<li>Supports all the modern browsers</li>\n<li>Support and Free upgrade</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</p>\n<h3 id=\"item-description_available_options\">Available Options</h3>\n</p>\n<h4 id=\"item-description_options_module\">Module Tab</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Source</strong> </li>\n<li><strong>Select Layout</strong> </li>\n<li><strong>Slider Content Type</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Slider Content Max Width (px)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Nav Button Position</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Slider Nav Type</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Upload Prev Image</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Upload Next Image</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Prev Button Text</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Prev Button Text</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Next Button Text</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Load Animate CSS</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Load Animate CSS</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Category(Joomla)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Order(Joomla)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Authors(Joomla)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Featured Articles(Joomla)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Count(Joomla)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Categories(K2)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Featured items(K2)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Count(K2)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Hover Style Type</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Card Iamge</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Padding</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Info Padding</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"item-description_options_jarticle\">Joomla Article</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Order</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Authors</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Featured Articles</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Count</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Categories</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Featured items</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Count</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Hover Style Type</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Card Iamge</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Padding</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Info Padding</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"item-description_options_k2\">K2 Article</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Categories</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Featured items</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Count</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Hover Style Type</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Card Iamge</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Padding</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Info Padding</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"item-description_options_card\">Card Settings</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hover Style Type</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Card Iamge</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Padding</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Info Padding</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"item-description_options_mcard\">Material Card Settings</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hover Style Type</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Card Title</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Card Excerpt</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Bottom Button</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Padding</strong></li>\n<li><strong></strong></li>\n<li><strong>Card Info Padding</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Details Button Text</strong></li>\n<li><strong>More Button Color</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Navigation Button Color</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"item-description_options_responsive\">Responsive Settings</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Add Resonsive Class</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Item in Large Desktops</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Nav(Large Desktops)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Item in Desktops</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Nav(Desktops)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Item in Tablets</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Nav(Tablet)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Item in Mobile</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Show Nav(Mobile)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"item-description_options_style\">Style Settings</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Slider Background Color</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Background Opacity</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Slider Content Color</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Details Button Light Color</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Details Button Deep Color</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Nav Text Color</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Nav Background Color</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dot Color</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Active Dot Color</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Slider Top Margin</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Slider Bottom Margin</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Slider Top Padding</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Slider Bottom Padding</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"item-description_options_slider\">Slider Settings</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Enabled Loop</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Item Margin</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Stage Padding</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Enabled Nav</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Enabled Dots</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Enabled Autoplay</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Autoplay Timeout</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Auto Width</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Smart Speed</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Free Drag</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Pull Drag</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Mouse Drag</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Touch Drag</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Auto Height</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Enabled Lazy Load</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Lazy Content</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Center item</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Enabled Video</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Set video Width</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Set video height</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Autoplay Timeout</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Autoplay Hover Pause</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Nav Rewind</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dot Each</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Dot Data</strong></li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"http://logichunt.com/product/joomla-content-slider/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\"