ound</strong></a></li>\n <li><i  style=\"color:#ff4b39;opacity:1;\"  class=\"fa fa-check-circle-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/product/joomla-ripple-effect/\"><strong> Joomla Ripple Effect</strong></a></li>\n\n    <li><i  style=\"color:#ff4b39; opacity:1;\"  class=\"fa fa-check-circle-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/product/joomla-parallax-typed/\"><strong> Joomla Parallax Typed</strong></a></li>\n \n</ul>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"LogicHunt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4988:\"<div class=\"alert alert-info lgx-alert text-center\" role=\"alert\">\n<h2>You may be amazed by our more stylish section builder items. Just make a visit</h2>\n<p><a style=\"font-size: 20px;\" class=\"btn btn-info\" href=\"http://logichunt.com/product/joomla-particle-background/\"><strong> Joomla Particle Background</strong></a></p>\n<p><a style=\"font-size: 20px;\" class=\"btn btn-info\" href=\"http://logichunt.com/product/joomla-parallax-typed/\"><strong> Joomla Parallax Typed</strong></a></p>\n<p><a style=\"font-size: 20px;\" class=\"btn btn-info\" href=\"http://logichunt.com/product/joomla-ripple-effect/\"><strong> Joomla Ripple Effect</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"lgx-margin-lg\"></div>\n<h2>Parallax Scroll is the Amazing Section Builder Joomla Module to Build a Responsive and Attractive Section with Background Parallax Scrolling Effect on Your Joomla! Site. Very simple to install and use. </h2>\n<h4>It is a Simple but most Powerful &#038; Essential Parallax section builder module that used more than 2000+ live Joomla! website in the world.</h4>\n<p>Joomla Parallax Scroll is a Ultimate Parallax Section Builder Module for Joomla. An Easiest Way to Get a Parallax Scrolling Background Image with Desired Message, Title, Logo and Desired Message on Your Joomla Website.</p>\n<div class=\"lgx-product-section-header\">\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-angellist\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Exclusive Feature</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Responsive Parallax Background.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Easy and Quick Installation. </div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> HTML markup Support on the Content.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Multiple Instances on One Page.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Control Section Width, Margin, Padding and Background.</div>\n</p></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Background Overlay Color with Opacity.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Multi-lingual Supported.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i>  Module Style Overrides Available form Template.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-success\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Super lightweight and easy to use.</div>\n<div class=\"alert alert-info\" role=\"alert\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\" ></i> Joomla 3.7 Ready.</div>\n</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"lgx-product-section-header\">\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-eye\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Product Screenshot</h3>\n</di