\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"LogicHunt\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2792:\"<h2>Joomla Parallax Content Slider Module to Build a Responsive Joomla! Article Carousel Slider with Parallax Scrolling Background Effect.</h3>\n<h4>Parallax Content Slider Allows You to Display Joomla! Article with Stunning &#038; Unique Look as well as Incredible Functionality with Beautiful Parallax Scrolling Background Effect.</h4>\n<p>Parallax Content Slider is a Responsive carousel slider module with touch swipe navigation. This module allows slide your articles from Joomla! categories with image &#038; stunning design. The module’s rich &#038; user-friendly back-end configuration provides more control over the module.</p>\n<h4>Parallax Content Slider also supports YouTube or Vimeo videos that helps to display your video galleries.</h4>\n<div class=\"lgx-product-section-header\">\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-angellist\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Exclusive Feature</h3>\n</div>\n<ul>\n<li>Joomla 3.6 Ready</li>\n<li>Responsive &amp; Touch Friendly Slides.</li>\n<li>Multiple Instances on One Page.</li>\n<li>Control Displayable Slides Item According Device Width(Viewport)</li>\n<li>Display Slides Card With Material Design.</li>\n<li>Easy and elegant display of article.</li>\n<li>Four Different layout are available: Default, Video, Card and Material Card.</li>\n<li>Show multiple slides in a carousel layout.</li>\n<li>Style(CSS) Overrides available form Template </li>\n<li>Fully Responsive &amp; Mobile Ready Slides Card.</li>\n<li>Control visibility of Card Title, Image &amp; Text.</li>\n<li>Display Slides with Article Title, Intro Image &amp; Text</li>\n<li>Display Full Article Content.</li>\n<li>Support YouTube/Vimeo videos.</li>\n<li>Background Image &amp; color for Slider Area.</li>\n<li>Control Slider Pagination Color.</li>\n<li>Set Image or Text  Navigation button.</li>\n<li>Control Dots navigation and prev/next buttons.</li>\n<li>Infinity Slides loop.</li>\n<li>Touch swipe navigation</li>\n<li>Slider auto pause OnHover</li>\n<li>Customizable Slides direction</li>\n<li>Carousel Slider</li>\n<li>Touch and Drag Support.</li>\n<li>Strong Administrator Settings </li>\n<li>Excellent CSS3 Transitions</li>\n<li>Valid HTML &amp; SEO friendly</li>\n<li>Editable styles with pure CSS or LESS ( Gulp File is available )</li>\n<li>Supports all the modern browsers</li>\n<li>Support and Free upgrade</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"lgx-margin-sm\"></div>\n<div class=\"lgx-product-section-header\">\n<h3><i class=\"fa fa-rocket\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Visit Live Demo </h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6\">\n        <a href=\"http://logichunt.com/joomlademo/module/parallax-slider\" target=\"_blank\"> <img  src=\"http://logichunt.com/wp-content/uploads/product/live-demo.jpg\" alt=\"Product Image\" /></a></p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"lgx-margin-lg\"></div>\n<div class=\"lgx-margin-sm\"></div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"http://logichunt.com/product/joomla-parallax-content-slider/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"2139\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";