r social media profiles in Joomla.</p>\n<div class=\"clearfix\" style=\"margin-top: 5px\"></div>\n<h3>Available Feature</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>* Fully responsive and mobile ready.</li>\n<li>* Easy to use and customize</li>\n<li>* Tooltip with Social Media Name</li>\n<li>* Control Tooltip Style</li>\n<li>* Control Logo Size &#038; margin</li>\n<li>* Section Background Color</li>\n<li>*Attractive Hover Style: Default, Gray, Zoom In, GrayScale.</li>\n<li>* Control Social Area Margin &#038; Padding</li>\n<li>* Enable/ Disable Socila Media</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"clearfix\" style=\"margin-top: 50px\"></div>\n<h3>Available Social Networking sites</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>witter</li>\n<li>Facebook</li>\n<li>Behance</li>\n<li>Digg</li>\n<li>Dribble</li>\n<li>Flickr</li>\n<li>Github</li>\n<li>Google+</li>\n<li>Linkedin</li>\n<li>Myspace</li>\n<li>Reddit</li>\n<li>Soundcloud</li>\n<li>Tumblr</li>\n<li>Vimeo</li>\n<li>Youtube</li>\n<li><strong>&#8230;&#8230;..Here You Can Suggest.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"http://logichunt.com/product/joomla-social-connect-link/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"590\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"